00:00:11.290 --> 00:00:24.660
 Cinnamon is an aromatic plant with medicinal properties, which will help you lose weight, 

00:00:24.660 --> 00:00:28.240
 besides to purify the organism and to maintain controlled the glucose and the cholesterol. 

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:31.420
 To get the most benefits you need to know how to prepare a good 

00:00:31.420 --> 00:00:35.090
 cinnamon infusion, a healthy and very light recipe that will allow you to include cinnamon 

00:00:35.090 --> 00:00:36.090
 in your daily diet. 

00:00:36.090 --> 00:00:39.250
 If you suffer from indigestion or slow digestion, if you have cardiovascular problems, or if 

00:00:39.250 --> 00:00:42.430
 You need to clean your body, this cinnamon tea will feel like a glove. 

00:00:42.430 --> 00:00:44.380
 To prepare it you will need the following ingredients 

00:00:44.380 --> 00:00:46.340
 a liter of water a cinnamon stick 

00:00:46.340 --> 00:00:48.540
 Preparation First boil the liter of water, 

00:00:48.540 --> 00:00:50.980
 Add the cinnamon and let stand for 10 minutes, 

00:00:50.980 --> 00:00:51.980
 Strain and serve, 

00:00:51.980 --> 00:00:55.140
 You can drink it both hot and cold. If you prefer you can add cinnamon to tea 

00:00:55.140 --> 00:00:56.850
 green or black tea, which you usually consume. 

00:00:56.850 --> 00:01:00.760
 They drink up to three cups of cinnamon tea daily, one in the morning, one after 

00:01:00.760 --> 00:01:02.720
 noon, and the last one after dinner. 

00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:03.750
 Keep in mind that while cinnamon tea has properties that can help you get off 

00:01:03.750 --> 00:01:07.720
 weight, it will not help if you do not supplement it with diet and exercise. 

00:01:07.720 --> 00:01:38.740
 Also, remember that despite its magnificent medicinal properties, cinnamon also 

00:01:38.740 --> 00:02:08.640
 has contraindications in certain circumstances such as pregnancy, breastfeeding or if you suffer 

00:02:08.640 --> 00:02:38.540
 a gastroduodenal ulcer, so it is always advisable to recommend medical consultation 

00:02:38.540 --> 00:02:47.739
 before consumption 

